{
  "stem": "22944.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, that-- that is a horrendous story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Horrendous story.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because he survived three days before the liberation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Because the Russians-- they did not know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Germans, they may need them to exchange the Russian army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the guard was panicky, and he shot them all.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Where was he, at that time?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he was a strong man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was quite-- he was 18, he was quite a healthy young-- young man.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He could have been alive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Also could have my father been alive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he was, till the last two or three days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then apparently, the guard, who was trying run away, did not know what to do.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everybody's gone, he didn't know what to do with the prisoners.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he shot them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, she went to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't tell you about my brother, but, of course, my brother tried to come back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The way he was caught-- he was in Hungary, then things become bad in Hungary, and he wanted to come back to Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on the border, he was caught with my sister, and he was taken away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not quite sure was my sister together on his own.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But my sister was in Hungary with my family, and then she was caught and gone on the Eichmann march, where she perished on the-- she was only 15 or so.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was very young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But she was very delicate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She was a very, very unusual young woman.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She was a pianist and a singer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Very, very gifted.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She was probably gifted-- the most gifted of all of us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Very bright girl.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she was very delicate, as well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she died from the march.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Gertie, my mother, and we-- we survived that, uh--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--Cellar.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
